{"data":[{"date":"07:44 18/08","title":"Ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, Emery v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/chiu-ap-luc-chi-trich-emery-van-quyet-khong-thay-doi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd v\u1eabn s\u1ebd trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby London l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea t\u1ed1i nay.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Arsenal th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19 d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Manchester City. </span>M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi sai l\u1ea7m chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi \u00f4ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u1ef1 s\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng pressing xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-arsenal-bi-chi-trich-hoc-doi-man-city-172-194568.html\" target=\"_blank\">c\u1ee7a Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Man City \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal</span> tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eaft h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech chuy\u1ec1n sai \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u1ed1t l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal, quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal, quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/chiu-ap-luc-chi-trich-emery-van-quyet-khong-thay-doi-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge cho tr\u1eadn derby London g\u1eb7p Chelsea, Emery tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i Arsenal, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng v\u1eabn s\u1ebd trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n sao? T\u1ea1i sao anh ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ng\u1eafn v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 ho\u1eb7c hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh? B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ee9ng nh\u1eafc v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3 b\u1edfi khi c\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1p l\u1ef1c pressing l\u1edbn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin, b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua Man City, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang ta ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau tr\u1eadn derby London l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea t\u1ed1i nay, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m kh\u00e1c v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/unai-emery-vs-pep-guardiola-bao-gio-het-noi-am-anh-172-194477.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/unai-emery-vs-pep-guardiola-bao-gio-het-noi-am-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/unai-emery-vs-pep-guardiola-bao-gio-het-noi-am-anh-172-194477.html\">Unai Emery vs Pep Guardiola: Bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh?</span><br>\r\nUnai Emery m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pep Guardiola. \u0110\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n quen thu\u1ed9c m\u1ed7i khi hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau t\u1eeb Mestalla cho \u0111\u1ebfn Emirates.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2488","checkdouble":"194709"},{"date":"08:18 18/08","title":"Sao Arsenal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Wenger kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/24/sao-arsenal-da-deu-thay-cu-wenger-khong-biet-huan-luyen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau khi \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn hung tin v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Etihad.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Man City m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn hung tin khi Kevin De Bruyne d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t s\u00e2n Etihad n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nghi thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong v\u00f2ng ba th\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, Guardiola khuy\u00ean chia tay Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, Guardiola khuy\u00ean chia tay Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/de-bruyne-chan-thuong-nang-pep-guardiola-khuyen-tam-chia-tay-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kevin De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, HLV Pep Guardiola khuy\u00ean... t\u1ea1m chia tay Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">HLV Pep Guardiola nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng, v\u1eeba nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn l\u00fd do qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n cho De Bruyne, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n x\u1ee9 Catalonia: \u201cCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1eddng khi anh \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t 11 th\u00e1ng tr\u1eddi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng r\u1ed3i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 World Cup trong h\u00e8. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, trong khi con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cL\u1eddi khuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i cho ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u00ean t\u1ea1m r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Man City trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi m\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3 h\u01a1i trong 2-3 tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m th\u1ebf ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng tay giang r\u1ed9ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Man City s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Huddersfield Town. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u01a1n b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh Arsenal ngay t\u1ea1i Emirates.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2487","checkdouble":"194710"},{"date":"07:32 18/08","title":"HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafc Mesut Ozil t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-unai-emery-nhac-mesut-ozil-tich-cuc-tham-gia-phong-ngu-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o Mesut Ozil ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2>HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafc Mesut Ozil&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Arsene Wenger, HLV Unai Emery m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Arsenal ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Manchester City v\u00e0 Chelsea, &quot;ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7&quot; \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ozil\" title=\"Ozil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/hlv-unai-emery-nhac-mesut-ozil-tich-cuc-tham-gia-phong-ngu-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafc Mesut Ozil ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Mesut Ozil. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u00f4ng nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n: &quot;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. M\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;C\u00f3 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau, c\u1ea3 trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1eabn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf Ozil ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng HLV Unai Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, Ozil c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 10, ho\u1eb7c \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i r\u1ed3i b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng&quot; - Unai Emery nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Anh \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m th\u1ebf trong m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ozil l\u00e0m g\u00ec&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Arsenal vs Chelsea s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 23h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mesut Ozil:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-nhan-chi-trich-tham-te-tu-huyen-thoai-arsenal-172-194464.html\">Ozil nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch th\u1eadm t\u1ec7 t\u1eeb huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/neuer-phat-bieu-ve-ozil-va-quyet-dinh-giai-nghe-192-192607.html\">Neuer: &ldquo;Ozil c\u1ee9 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/a-172-192592.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u Mesut Ozil ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft &ldquo;l\u00e0m m\u00e0u&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/quoc-te/cdv-duc-bieu-tinh-bang-co-tho-nhi-ky-de-ung-ho-ozil-290-192417.html\">C\u0110V \u0110\u1ee9c bi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng c\u1edd Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ozil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tam-thu-cua-mesut-ozil-giot-nuoc-tran-ly-p2-389-192316.html\">T\u00e2m th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil: Gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00e0n ly (P2)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huy-diet-psg-emery-het-loi-ca-ngoi-ozil-172-192233.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t PSG, Emery h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Ozil</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2486","checkdouble":"194714"},{"date":"07:25 18/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (18/8/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1882018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 18/8 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\